channel.description: Scattered pages from an apocryphal diary

item.title: By: Jenny
item.dc:creator: Jenny
item.description: Enter the modem. Kim Motzart and I were thrilled that we could type to each other after school. I thought it was cool that she had a pet bunny and a pet skunk, with the stinker removed, of course.
